<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Kylian Mbappe scored the only goal as France scraped past Sweden 1-0 in their opening Nations League match.</p>

<p>The Paris Saint-Germain forward struck in the first half from a tight angle past Sweden's Robin Olsen.</p>

<p>Antoine Griezmann missed a last-minute penalty over the bar after a foul from Victor Lindelof.  </p>

